few questions to everyone and see if we can get a debate going.<br>
<br>
Status...<br>
<br>
...a touchy subject, I would be interested in the insight of the Domain <br>
of Santa Carla on the following questions:<br>
<br>
1.  Who does the Primogen of a Clan have the right to give or<br>
    take status from?  How much Status must that Primogen<br>
    possess to do alter the other's status?<br>
<br>
2.  Who can bestow status on anyone in the Domain?  How<br>
    much status does this action require?<br>
<br>
3.  Who can remove status on anyone in the Domain?  How<br>
    much status is required to do this?<br>
<br>
4.  Who can bestow negative status on anyone in the<br>
    Domain?  How much status is required to do this?<br>
<br>
5.  What happens to an Kindred who garners too much<br>
    negative status to the point that it balances out with their<br>
    positive status?<br>
<br>
6.  What are the duties of the Head Harpy?  Lesser Harpies?<br>
<br>
 I fully understand that the views that might be presented are your opinions .  I am interested in how divergent our views and understandings may have become over time.  <br>
<br>
